      "content": "## Staging 演示\n\n**URL:** `https://staging.example.com/acme/workflow`\n\n**自测:** 4/5 通过\n\n- ✅ Intake → Classify\n- ✅ Classify → Draft\n- ✅ Draft → HITL\n- ✅ HITL → Archive\n- ⏳ 飞书生产回调（待 HITL-3）"
